{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"क़सम है उन हवाओं की जो निरंतर भेजी जाती हैं!","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-mur'salāti ʿur'fan ","translations":["By the ones sent forth","one after another","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-mur'salāti","ʿur'fan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1590],[2,1590,2565]]}},{"name":"77:2","price":"फिर बहुत तेज़ चलने वाली हवाओं की क़सम!","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-ʿāṣifāti ʿaṣfan ","translations":["And the winds that blow","violently","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-ʿāṣifāti","ʿaṣfan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2905]]}},{"name":"77:3","price":"और बादलों को फैलाने वाली हवाओं[1] की क़सम!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"1. अर्थात जो हवाएँ अल्लाह के आदेशानुसार बादलों को फैलाती हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nāshirāti nashran ","translations":["And the ones that scatter","far and wide","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nāshirāti","nashran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2130],[2,2130,3365]]}},{"name":"77:4","price":"फिर सत्य और असत्य के बीच अंतर करने वाली चीज़[2] के साथ उतरने वाले फ़रिश्तों की क़सम!","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"2. अर्थात सत्यासत्य तथा वैध और अवैध के बीच अंतर करने के लिए आदेश लाते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-fāriqāti farqan ","translations":["And those who separate","(by the) Criterion","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-fāriqāti","farqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1600],[2,1600,2825]]}},{"name":"77:5","price":"फिर वह़्य[3] लेकर उतरने वाले फ़रिश्तों की क़सम!","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"3. अर्थात जो वह़्य (प्रकाशना) ग्रहण करके उसे रसूलों तक पहुँचाते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mul'qiyāti dhik'ran ","translations":["And those who bring down","(the) Reminder","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mul'qiyāti","dhik'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2905]]}},{"name":"77:6","price":"उज़्र (बहाना) समाप्त करने या डराने[4] के लिए।","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"4. अर्थात ईमान लाने वालों के लिये क्षमा का वचन तथा काफ़िरों के लिये यातना की सूचना लाते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿudh'ran aw nudh'ran ","translations":["(As) justification","or","warning","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿudh'ran","aw","nudh'ran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,820],[2,820,1190],[3,1190,2495]]}},{"name":"77:7","price":"निःसंदेह तुमसे जिस चीज़ का वादा किया जाता है, निश्चय वह होकर रहने वाली है।","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"innamā tūʿadūna lawāqiʿun ","translations":["Indeed, what","you are promised","will surely occur","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["innamā","tūʿadūna","lawāqiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2800],[3,2800,4175]]}},{"name":"77:8","price":"फिर जब तारे मिटा दिए जाएँगे।","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā al-nujūmu ṭumisat ","translations":["So when","the stars","are obliterated","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","al-nujūmu","ṭumisat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,2050],[3,2050,3185]]}},{"name":"77:9","price":"और जब आकाश फाड़ दिया जाएगा।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-samāu furijat ","translations":["And when","the heaven","is cleft asunder","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-samāu","furijat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,2760],[3,2760,3645]]}},{"name":"77:10","price":"और जब पर्वत उड़ा दिए जाएँगे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jibālu nusifat ","translations":["And when","the mountains","are blown away","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jibālu","nusifat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,1540],[3,1540,2685]]}},{"name":"77:11","price":"और जब रसूलों को निर्धारित समय पर एकत्र किया जाएगा।[5]","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"5. उनके तथा उनके समुदायों के बीच निर्णय करने के लिए, और रसूल गवाही देंगे।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-rusulu uqqitat ","translations":["And when","the Messengers","are gathered to their appointed time","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-rusulu","uqqitat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1450],[3,1450,2635]]}},{"name":"77:12","price":"किस दिन के लिए वे विलंबित किए गए हैं?","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"li-ayyi yawmin ujjilat ","translations":["For what","Day","are (these) postponed","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["li-ayyi","yawmin","ujjilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1630],[3,1630,2805]]}},{"name":"77:13","price":"निर्णय के दिन के लिए।","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"liyawmi al-faṣli ","translations":["For (the) Day","(of) Judgment","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["liyawmi","al-faṣli",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1685]]}},{"name":"77:14","price":"और आपको किस चीज़ ने अवगत कराया कि निर्णय का दिन क्या है?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā yawmu al-faṣli ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","(is the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","yawmu","al-faṣli",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,2820],[3,2820,3170],[4,3170,3780],[5,3780,4875]]}},{"name":"77:15","price":"उस दिन झुठलाने वालों के लिए बड़ा विनाश है।","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1410],[3,1410,2420],[4,2420,5855]]}},{"name":"77:16","price":"क्या हमने पहलों को विनष्ट नहीं किया?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nuh'liki al-awalīna ","translations":["Did not","We destroy","the former (people)","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nuh'liki","al-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,550],[2,550,1370],[3,1370,4525]]}},{"name":"77:17","price":"फिर हम उनके पीछे बाद वालों को भेजेंगे।[6]","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"6. अर्थात उन्हीं के समान यातना ग्रस्त कर देंगे।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma nut'biʿuhumu al-ākhirīna ","translations":["Then","We follow them up","(with) the later ones","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","nut'biʿuhumu","al-ākhirīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,2290],[3,2290,5325]]}},{"name":"77:18","price":"हम अपराधियों के साथ ऐसा ही करते हैं।","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kadhālika nafʿalu bil-muj'rimīna ","translations":["Thus","We deal","with the criminals","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["kadhālika","nafʿalu","bil-muj'rimīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1820],[3,1820,5145]]}},{"name":"77:19","price":"उस दिन झुठलाने वालों के लिए बड़ा विनाश है।","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1400],[2,1400,2460],[3,2460,6085]]}},{"name":"77:20","price":"क्या हमने तुम्हें एक तुच्छ पानी से पैदा नहीं किया?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alam nakhluqkkum min māin mahīnin ","translations":["Did not","We create you","from","a water","despicable","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","nakhluqkkum","min","māin","mahīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1940],[3,1940,2680],[4,2680,5670],[5,5670,8675]]}},{"name":"77:21","price":"फिर हमने उसे एक सुरक्षित ठिकाने में रखा।","arab